<Aside type="caution" title="Security Setup Required">
  <p><strong>pgflow ships with ZERO database permissions for client roles.</strong> Before using this method from client applications, you must:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Expose the <code>pgflow</code> schema in your PostgREST configuration</li>
    <li>Configure database permissions for <code>anon</code> or <code>authenticated</code> roles</li>
  </ul>

  <p>See the <a href="/reference/permissions/">Permissions reference</a> for complete setup instructions.</p>

  <p><em>Note: Edge worker uses service role by default and does not require this setup.</em></p>
</Aside>
